004package data;
005
006import kut.*;
007
008/** Global rank entry. */
009public class RkEntry {
010  /** Model identifier. */
011  public final String id;
012  /** Index of investor. */
013  public final int ix;
014  /**
015  Price, reference or deviation. It it is '[]', 'val' is not valid
016  and there is a message in log.
017  */
018  public final Opt<Integer> val;
019
020  /**
021  Constructor.
022  @param id  Model identifier.
023  @param ix  Index of investor.
024  @param val Price, reference or deviation. It it is '[]', 'val' is not valid
025             and there is a message in log.
026  */
027  public RkEntry (String id, int ix, Opt<Integer> val) {
028    this.id = id;
029    this.ix = ix;
030    this.val = val;
031  }
032
033  /**
034  JSON serialization.
035  @return JSON.
036  */
037  public String toJs () {
038    return Js.w(Arr.mk(
039      Js.w(id),
040      Js.w(ix),
041      Opt.toJs(val, Js::w)
042    ));
043  }
044}
